    <briefdescription>
<para>Context wrapper for KD-tree operations. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class encapsulates:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>input point data</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>nanoflann adaptor</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>KD-tree index</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>It provides convenient methods for nearest-neighbor and radius-based queries.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The input vectors must remain valid for the lifetime of this object. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
